  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2368326">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2368326/" class="title-link">神作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2368326"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/kara/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1102359-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kara/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">卡拉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-09-21"
      class="main-meta">2009-09-21 10:07:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2368326_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如果要用一个词来形容——神作；如果要用一句话来形容，没有知识面的狭隘，没有网络语的格调低下，没有流水化的描述，没有青涩的文笔和前后不统一的风格，总之没有一切网络小说可能出现的让我一眼看过久不会想看实体书的弊病。读完全作，从床上站起，在房间来回踱步，仔细回味...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2368326/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
